message.content: cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.DC, cs.COMM, cs.SY - This paper is primarily focused on the performance analysis of Ethernet Passive Optical Networks (EPONs) with gated-limited service discipline, which is a networking technology related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and communication systems (cs.COMM). The paper also involves the derivation of a mathematical formula for M/G/1 queue with vacation times, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of transmission window (TW) size on packet delay, which is a crucial aspect of data center (cs.DC) and system analysis (cs.SY).
